item.title: Whats any ip address and pass? Im new
item.dc:creator: @mod_SYN mod SYN
item.description:
@mod_SYN wrote:

what you do is go to "HELP"on the moparscape client when opened then go to “SERVER STATUS” and look at servers that are online then copy one then go to “FILE” on the Moparscape client and click "new server"then hit ctrl+v at the same time or ctrl then v and then click ok then go back to the server status page and look at the port then back to the client and go to file again then click new port and type in the port of the server
Example: Server IP:medievalfantasyscape.servegame.com Port:43594
Port 43594 is most common

Enjoy!
